trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when a check for sufficient available memory fails.
This class cannot be inherited.
Unlike <xref:System.OutOfMemoryException>, <xref:System.InsufficientMemoryException> is thrown before starting an operation, and thus does not imply state corruption.
trans-unit.target: 与不同<xref:System.OutOfMemoryException>，<xref:System.InsufficientMemoryException>在开始操作之前引发，并因此并不意味着状态损坏。

trans-unit.source: An application can catch this exception, throttle back its memory usage, and avoid actual out of memory conditions and their potential for corrupting program state.
trans-unit.target: 应用程序可以捕获此异常、 限制返回其内存使用量，并避免实际现成的内存情况和其可能会破坏程序状态。

trans-unit.source: This exception is thrown by the <xref:System.Runtime.MemoryFailPoint.%23ctor%2A> constructor when you specify a projected memory allocation larger than the amount of currently available memory.
trans-unit.target: 引发此异常<xref:System.Runtime.MemoryFailPoint.%23ctor%2A>构造函数时指定分配的内存大于当前可用的内存量。

trans-unit.source: Your program can catch the exception and either delay the task that needs the memory or execute it in smaller steps that require less memory.
trans-unit.target: 你的程序可捕获该异常，并请延迟需要的内存或执行在更小的步骤需要较少的内存中的任务。

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Runtime.MemoryFailPoint> class for a code example.
trans-unit.target: 请参阅<xref:System.Runtime.MemoryFailPoint>有关代码示例的类。

trans-unit.source: This exception is not included in the [.NET for Windows Store apps](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=247912) or the [Portable Class Library](~/docs/standard/cross-platform/cross-platform-development-with-the-portable-class-library.md), but it is thrown by some members that are.
trans-unit.target: 此异常未包含在[.NET for Windows Store 应用](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=247912)或[可移植类库](~/docs/standard/cross-platform/cross-platform-development-with-the-portable-class-library.md)，但它将引发的某些成员。

trans-unit.source: To catch the exception in that case, write a `catch` statement for <xref:System.OutOfMemoryException> instead.
trans-unit.target: 若要在这种情况下捕获异常，编写`catch`语句<xref:System.OutOfMemoryException>相反。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.InsufficientMemoryException" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.InsufficientMemoryException" /> class with a system-supplied message that describes the error.

This constructor initializes the <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A> property of the new instance to a system-supplied message that describes the error, such as "Insufficient available memory to meet the expected demands of an operation at this time.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数初始化<xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>属性的新实例为系统提供的消息描述错误，例如"可用内存不足以满足这一次操作的预期的要求。

trans-unit.source: Please try again later."
trans-unit.target: 请稍后再试。"

trans-unit.source: This message takes into account the current system culture.
trans-unit.target: 此消息将当前系统区域性考虑在内。

trans-unit.source: The message that describes the exception.
The caller of this constructor is required to ensure that this string has been localized for the current system culture.
The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
If the <c>innerException</c> parameter is not <see langword="null" />, the current exception is raised in a <see langword="catch" /> block that handles the inner exception.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.InsufficientMemoryException" /> class with a specified error message and a reference to the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 因前一个异常而直接引发的异常应在 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性中包含对前一个异常的引用。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is passed into the constructor, or `null` if the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property does not supply the inner exception value to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性返回的值与传递到构造函数中的值相同；或者，如果 `null` 属性没有向构造函数提供内部异常值，则为 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>。
